		<desc>Identifies the hazardous material warnings. The hazardous material warning consists of a graphic(s) (e.g fire icon, poison icon, etc.), the hazardous material name, and the sequence number which identifies the order in which the hazardous material warnings are included in the safety summary. See Appendix A for further information on hazardous material warnings.</desc>
		<source>4.3.10.1</source>
