		<long>Usable on code explanation</long>
		<desc>Identifies the useable on code paragraphs in the ipb foreword</desc>
		<source>3.5.8 MIL-PRF-38807</source>
		<contmdl>(title, warning*, caution?, note?, (para, note?)?, (step1, step1+)?, subpara1*)</contmdl>
